{"tid":1419862,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣同勇武唔該入黎］18區老友記送口罩","createTime":"2019-08-06T02:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T12:34:59.000Z","uid":239496,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a981e3878a2ee692ef0bf4c87eddb688f1e89b28","tid":1419862,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:53:00.000Z","msg":"係黃大仙見到唔少老人家冇口罩要硬食催淚彈<br />\n而應該覺醒嘅人都已經覺醒左<br />\n所以下一步要唸點樣以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以最少成本</span></span>打最大嘅民意戰<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">主流媒體</span></span>取回話語權<br />\n證明我地<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係暴徒</span></span><br />\n我地勇武嘅已經進化左<br />\n呢一刻，文宣需要再進化，而我地要做更多對呢個社會有幫助嘅事實<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">團結社會嘅大多數</span></span><br />\n令到最多人企係我地呢邊<br />\n即使唔係和理非、甚至藍絲<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦話<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">條條大路通羅馬</span></span><br />\n所以我地要開闢新嘅大路（唔好話我左膠發過N次夢）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">做實事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n譴責警方濫用催淚彈，贈送口罩給十八區嘅老友記（越藍嘅地區越要送）：有意打區選嘅組織可以送。但記住，一定要係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">後生仔</span></span>去送，我地唔係冇啦啦送口罩，我地要同老友記<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">傾計</span></span>！<br />\n點解要送口罩，解釋返點解我地有五大訴求，點解<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反送中</span></span>，點解<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反政府</span></span>，點解呢個政府<span style=\"color: red;\">不得不反</span><br />\n<br />\n依家政府想打返民意牌，甚至想日日記招，我地出民間記者招待會係對衝唔到嘅（除非有陳方安生、王永平、前終院大法官呢類較<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中立嘅人物</span></span>企台），講嘅內容唔好限於示威遊行<br />\n<br />\n所以做一啲<span style=\"color: red;\">規模震撼嘅實事</span>可以直接擊垮政府嘅民意戰策略，反Cut，呢個係超短期手段，幾下流都要用，<span style=\"color: red;\">只要對我地終極目標有幫助嘅手段都要用</span>，令到民意真正<span style=\"color: red;\">覺醒</span><br />\n先係真正嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山</span>，先可以幫前線兄弟流<span style=\"color: red;\">流更少嘅血</span>，打更遠嘅仗。如果你有必死嘅決心，就用黎對抗老解！呢個唔係戰役，係戰爭！係最終戰爭發生之前， 我地即刻要令民意變成反政府先，呢個係每一次歷史革命嘅基礎。<br />\n<br />\n只有民意覺醒，推翻政府先係合情合理。<br />\n<br />\n最後，短期目標<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span><br />\n<br />\n終極目標<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6258515e233a4694ded0d8019fbf8f042825e04b","tid":1419862,"uid":239496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:57:58.000Z","msg":"勇武已經Be water<br />\n雞蛋打唔爛高牆嘅話<br />\n我要民意都好似洪水咁澎拜<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">衝冧高牆</span>"},{"pid":"83134e5661a4f2eb9d3379a8c93defe2e78dc778","tid":1419862,"uid":239496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:59:04.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZ8E3HB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZ8E3HB.gif&h=695f9996&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aadc274124cdf1c3f6a0a0afd2ea43e9f6d54518","tid":1419862,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:03:03.000Z","msg":"不割席<br />\n<br />\n諗返轉頭，記唔記得點解要勇武？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1419827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1419827</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"94f253c2ef148e18ce09acff2e9fbd465e3161b7","tid":1419862,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:05:05.000Z","msg":"經濟牌嘅打法<br />\n<br />\n[[[[快入打]]]  輿論戰要打經濟牌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1419439\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1419439</a><br />\n- 分